<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="quarrel-vi">quarrel <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kwɒrəl/    美 /'kwɔːrəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>争吵；吵架：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>quarrel with sb about / over sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She quarrelled with her brother over his schoolwork.
她因弟弟的功课而与他发生了争执。</p></div></div>